<b>- Hello. - Hello.</b>

87
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:07,080
<b>These are so pretty.</b>

88
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:10,080
<b>What is the symbolic meaning of tulips?</b>

89
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:12,960
<b>Oh, it's "confession of love."</b>

