00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:18,360
<b>Would you like some?</b>

91
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:30,010
<b>My one last chance.</b>

92
00:11:43,150 --> 00:11:46,620
<b>You have no idea how much effort I've made to date.</b>

93
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:49,430
<b>A couple goes on a trip after they break up.</b>

94
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:52,720
<b>While they were still together,</b>

95
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:55,870
<b>they saved up some money to go on a trip together someday.</b>

96
00:11:55,930 --> 00:11:58,890
<b>They go on a trip after they break up? Together?</b>

97
00:11:58,890 --> 00:12:00,460
<b>No, separately.</b>

98
00:12:00,460 --> 00:12:01,760
<b>Really?</b>

99
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:04,640
<b>And then? What happens?</b>

100
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:09,750
<b>I did my very best.</b>

101
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:17,050
<b>But why now?</b>

102
00:12:17,510 --> 00:12:20,480
<b>You never acted on it, so why now? Why this way?</b>

103
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:22,860
<b>Because I couldn't win his heart no matter how hard I tried.</b>

104
00:12:25,090 --> 00:12:29,060
<b>I just couldn't make it happen. What was I supposed to do?</b>

105
00:12:29,330 --> 00:12:30,570
<b>You see,</b>

106
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:34,500
<b>I actually had a crush on you.</b>

107
00:12:36,330 --> 00:12:37,510
<b>What?</b>

108
00:12:38,830 --> 00:12:40,940
<b>For a very long time.</b>

109
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:44,810
<b>I didn't know.</b>

110
00:12:46,380 --> 00:12:48,450
<b>What if you knew, Eun Seop?</b>

111
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:55,260
<b>Nothing...</b>

112
00:12:56,850 --> 00:12:58,890
<b>would've changed.</b>

113
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:06,330
<b>- Hey. - I didn't get into any colleges.</b>

114
00:13:06,330 --> 00:13:08,840
<b>- Gosh. - You can try again next year.</b>

115
00:13:16,310 --> 00:13:18,870
<b>- Hey. - Do you want to do this with me?</b>

116
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,180
<b>Hey, Eun Seop!</b>

117
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,980
<b>- Hey, come on. - No.</b>

118
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:24,580
<b>You can have this. I got too many. Come, I'll buy you jjajangmyeon.</b>

119
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:27,350
<b>Come on. Everyone's waiting. Hurry.</b>

120
00:13:27,350 --> 00:13:29,360
<b>Hey, come on. Quick.</b>

121
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:32,760
<b>- Right? - Oh, gosh!</b>

122
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:37,330
<b>Sure, I may have had many chances, but so what?</b>

123
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:42,710
<b>The timing was always off.</b>

124
00:13:46,540 --> 00:13:49,450
<b>As if I shouldn't exist in his life.</b>

125
00:14:11,490 --> 00:14:14,800
<b>Eun Seop! Lim Eun Seop!</b>

126
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:17,100
<b>You said you'd buy me a gaming console with your savings.</b>

127
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:19,240
<b>- Did you bring it? - Yes, it's in my backpack.</b>

128
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:21,100
<b>Oh, nice!</b>

129
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:22,500
<b>Girls, say hi. This is my brother.</b>

130
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:24,370
<b>- Hello. - He'll buy us jjajangmyeon.</b>

131
00:14:24,370 --> 00:14:25,840
<b>Bye! Let's go.</b>

132
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:27,580
<b>- I'll call you. - See you later.</b>

133
00:14:27,740 --> 00:14:29,990
<b>Come on. Let's go!</b>

134
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,540
<b>(Good Night Bookstore)</b>

135
00:14:49,060 --> 00:14:52,430
<b>Oh, right. I heard that hobo runs this bookstore now.</b>

136
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:55,470
<b>- "Hobo"? - That guy, you know.</b>

137
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:57,350
<b>The one who used to live in the mountains.</b>

138
00:15:00,980 --> 00:15:02,880
<b>All right, let's go!</b>

139
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:04,150
<b>Okay.</b>

140
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,360
<b>Son, what do you feel like eating?</b>

141
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:17,570
<b>Well, something with meat?</b>

142
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:29,110
<b>That's why I couldn't do anything.</b>

143
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:32,920
<b>I couldn't talk to him...</b>

144
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:35,580
<b>or even call him once.</b>

145
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:42,190
<b>But I suddenly became brave...</b>

146
00:15:43,490 --> 00:15:45,090
<b>after you came.</b>

147
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:47,860
<b>What?</b>

148
00:15:48,090 --> 00:15:49,970
<b>After you came here,</b>

149
00:15:50,430 --> 00:15:53,540
<b>I suddenly became anxious and determined.</b>

150
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:57,070
<b>I wanted to get in your way and be mean to you.</b>

151
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:59,240
<b>What did you say?</b>

152
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:02,240
<b>Be honest.</b>

153
00:16:03,110 --> 00:16:05,710
<b>There was a time when you intentionally got in my way.</b>

154
00:16:42,610 --> 00:16:45,350
<b>Hey, Bo Yeong!</b>

155
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,420
<b>Hey, why are you crying?</b>

156
00:16:49,450 --> 00:16:51,350
<b>Why are you crying? Did something happen?</b>

157
00:16:51,350 --> 00:16:55,000
<b>Because of what happened in the AV room earlier, right?</b>

158
00:16:56,030 --> 00:16:58,330
<b>Mok Hae Won made a move on Lim Eun Seop, didn't she?</b>

159
00:16:59,190 --> 00:17:02,660
<b>Gosh, I never liked that girl.</b>

160
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:04,830
<b>That sneaky girl.</b>

161
00:17:04,830 --> 00:17:07,140
<b>Gosh, how dare she?</b>

162
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:09,950
<b>No, never.</b>

163
00:17:10,910 --> 00:17:13,640
<b>- What? - I never got in your way.</b>

164
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:15,220
<b>Not even once.</b>

165
00:17:16,450 --> 00:17:19,150
<b>You never made a move on him deliberately,</b>

166
00:17:19,210 --> 00:17:21,780
<b>knowing that I had a crush on him?</b>

167
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:23,290
<b>No, never.</b>

168
00:17:24,250 --> 00:17:26,960
<b>I speculated that you probably liked him,</b>

169
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:29,530
<b>but I didn't know that Eun Seop was your crush.</b>

170
00:17:30,290 --> 00:17:32,070
<b>You know what?</b>

171
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:35,570
<b>I have a crush on someone.</b>

172
00:17:36,130 --> 00:17:38,940
<b>I like him so much!</b>

173
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:42,580
<b>Never.</b>

174
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:49,820
<b>That's why I can't understand you at all.</b>

175
00:17:50,410 --> 00:17:53,520
<b>Why would you become so mean because of me?</b>

176
00:17:56,350 --> 00:17:57,530
<b>Bo Yeong.</b>

177
00:17:59,120 --> 00:18:02,460
<b>What made you so twisted?</b>

178
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:18,010
<b>Yes.</b>

179
00:18:19,170 --> 00:18:20,480
<b>I found her.</b>

180
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:24,720
<b>No, don't worry. I'll bring her down.</b>

181
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:26,420
<b>Okay.</b>

182
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:34,860
<b>Follow me, and don't fall behind.</b>

183
00:19:09,830 --> 00:19:11,160
<b>Out of the way.</b>

184
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:13,470
<b>Move out of the way, everyone!</b>

185
00:19:22,370 --> 00:19:23,510
<b>What?</b>

186
00:19:24,410 --> 00:19:25,670
<b>Do you need anything?</b>

187
00:19:25,670 --> 00:19:27,540
<b>Just tell me the terms of the deal.</b>

188
00:19:27,540 --> 00:19:30,850
<b>Oh, right. I was supposed to tell you that.</b>

189
00:19:39,590 --> 00:19:41,420
<b>What? You don't like it?</b>

190
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:44,090
<b>- No. - Then you don't have to come.</b>

191
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:46,740
<b>Who cares about book clubs anyway?</b>

192
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:51,740
<b>Fine.</b>

193
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:20,840
<b>You're early.</b>

194
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:26,810
<b>Thank you.</b>

195
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:36,820
<b>I hear you're seeing Shim Myeong Yeo these days.</b>

196
00:20:37,510 --> 00:20:38,650
<b>Yes.</b>

197
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:44,190
<b>And she's holed up in the woods somewhere in Gangwon Province?</b>

198
00:20:48,320 --> 00:20:52,930
<b>You know, I want you to focus on me...</b>

199
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:55,400
<b>whether it's as a writer...</b>

200
00:20:56,270 --> 00:20:57,370
<b>or as a woman.</b>

201
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:01,810
<b>- What? - I want you to stop seeing her.</b>

202
00:21:02,670 --> 00:21:05,210
<b>I'm not telling you not to publish her book.</b>

203
00:21:05,570 --> 00:21:07,380
<b>Her book will be published...</b>

204
00:21:07,380 --> 00:21:09,380
<b>whether you see her or not.</b>

205
00:21:09,680 --> 00:21:11,580
<b>So just publish her book...</b>

206
00:21:11,580 --> 00:21:13,290
<b>without seeing her.</b>

207
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:16,430
<b>Okay? Can you do that?</b>

208
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:21,030
<b>It's all true, Yun Taek.</b>

209
00:21:23,860 --> 00:21:26,300
<b>- Can I get some water, please? - Coming up.</b>

210
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,540
<b>What do you mean?</b>

211
00:21:27,930 --> 00:21:30,540
<b>And they say I'm the next Shim Myeong Yeo?</b>

212
00:21:31,230 --> 00:21:32,740
<b>Unbelievable.</b>

213
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:34,800
<b>What does she have that I don't?</b>

214
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:37,270
<b>Is my writing not as good as hers?</b>

215
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:38,570
<b>Am I not as good-looking as she is?</b>

216
00:21:38,570 --> 00:21:41,580
<b>Fine, she was born earlier, I'll give her that.</b>

217
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:44,920
<b>Have you even heard the rumors?</b>

218
00:21:46,350 --> 00:21:47,490
<b>You haven't?</b>

219
00:21:47,780 --> 00:21:49,890
<b>At the peak of her career,</b>

220
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:52,530
<b>she suddenly quit writing and went back to her hometown.</b>

221
00:21:53,760 --> 00:21:55,320
<b>What did they say?</b>

222
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:57,790
<b>Everything people say about me is true.</b>

223
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:58,930
<b>Right.</b>

224
00:21:58,990 --> 00:22:00,400
<b>That's the truth.</b>

225
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:06,480
<b>They say she had a fling with her brother-in-law,</b>

226
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:10,650
<b>and that's why her sister killed her husband.</b>

227
00:22:13,140 --> 00:22:14,680
<b>Believe what they say.</b>

228
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:21,290
<b>So you didn't know?</b>

229
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:26,390
<b>Then why did you two break up?</b>

230
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:27,800
<b>Gosh, it's hot.</b>

231
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:32,270
<b>Excuse me. I asked for water, not broth.</b>

232
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:33,500
<b>Okay.</b>

233
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:35,070
<b>Cha Yun Taek.</b>

234
00:22:36,730 --> 00:22:37,870
<b>Cha...</b>

235
00:22:40,170 --> 00:22:41,310
<b>Myeong Yeo!</b>

236
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:43,140
<b>Myeong Yeo!</b>

237
00:22:46,070 --> 00:22:47,380
<b>Answer me.</b>

238
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:50,590
<b>You're very persistent.</b>

239
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:53,790
<b>Just tell me the reason.</b>

240
00:22:53,980 --> 00:22:55,320
<b>Is that so hard?</b>

241
00:22:55,850 --> 00:22:56,990
<b>Yun Taek.</b>

242
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:00,800
<b>Have a good life.</b>

243
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:04,230
<b>Have a good life.</b>

244
00:23:04,430 --> 00:23:05,630
<b>Get married like you've always wanted,</b>

245
00:23:05,630 --> 00:23:06,860
<b>have kids like you've always dreamed of,</b>

246
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:09,170
<b>and live happily ever after.</b>

247
00:23:10,230 --> 00:23:12,370
<b>Myeong Yeo.</b>

248
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:16,280
<b>Please be happy. Forget an idiot like me, okay?</b>

249
00:23:16,870 --> 00:23:19,580
<b>Myeong Yeo.</b>

250
00:23:19,780 --> 00:23:21,080
<b>Let go!</b>

251
00:23:28,420 --> 00:23:30,490
<b>I'm going to do everything with you.</b>

252
00:23:35,820 --> 00:23:37,670
<b>I'm going to do everything with you.</b>

253
00:23:43,130 --> 00:23:44,770
<b>Like this.</b>

254
00:24:08,660 --> 00:24:09,800
<b>I'm...</b>

255
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,300
<b>not.</b>

256
00:24:31,710 --> 00:24:34,520
<b>Everything people say about me is true.</b>

257
00:24:34,850 --> 00:24:36,220
<b>That's the truth.</b>

258
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:40,300
<b>Believe what they say.</b>

259
00:26:17,390 --> 00:26:18,890
<b>- Hae Won. - You woke up?</b>

260
00:26:18,890 --> 00:26:20,030
<b>Yes.</b>

261
00:26:20,360 --> 00:26:23,290
<b>Are you feeling okay?</b>

262
00:26:23,290 --> 00:26:24,760
<b>You didn't catch a cold or anything?</b>

263
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:26,170
<b>No, I didn't.</b>

264
00:26:26,630 --> 00:26:27,870
<b>How are you?</b>

265
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,240
<b>I'm good.</b>

266
00:26:31,500 --> 00:26:34,010
<b>Did you talk to...</b>

267
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:35,710
<b>- Did it... - It went well.</b>

268
00:26:36,910 --> 00:26:38,180
<b>That's great.</b>

269
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:46,450
<b>What? Don't tell me you're sleepy again.</b>

270
00:26:46,550 --> 00:26:47,920
<b>I am.</b>

271
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:52,490
<b>I thought you had insomnia. Or was it mythomania?</b>

272
00:26:52,490 --> 00:26:54,420
<b>- I do. - You have mythomania?</b>

273
00:26:54,420 --> 00:26:56,460
<b>No, I have insomnia.</b>

274
00:27:00,100 --> 00:27:02,830
<b>No, you can't fall asleep now. Get up.</b>

275
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:04,330
<b>- Hae Won. - What?</b>

276
00:27:04,330 --> 00:27:05,700
<b>Let me take a short nap.</b>

277
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:07,100
<b>What short nap?</b>

278
00:27:07,100 --> 00:27:09,200
<b>You slept all this time. Get up already.</b>

279
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:11,010
<b>I'm bored. Come on.</b>

280
00:27:11,010 --> 00:27:12,210
<b>What?</b>

281
00:27:12,470 --> 00:27:13,650
<b>Hey.</b>

282
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:15,950
<b>Hey.</b>

283
00:27:17,180 --> 00:27:18,850
<b>- Get up. - What?</b>

284
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:20,420
<b>My eyes.</b>

285
00:27:21,620 --> 00:27:23,390
<b>Come on, get up.</b>

286
00:27:23,390 --> 00:27:26,260
<b>Get up. Come on, get up.</b>

287
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:28,060
<b>- Hey. - Get up.</b>

288
00:27:28,060 --> 00:27:29,260
<b>I'm going to make you into the Joker.</b>

289
00:27:29,260 --> 00:27:31,070
<b>Okay, I'll get up.</b>

290
00:27:32,230 --> 00:27:35,130
<b>Hey, no! Get up.</b>

291
00:27:35,130 --> 00:27:37,100
<b>You're really not going to get up? Come on.</b>

292
00:27:37,100 --> 00:27:38,970
<b>Hey! Get up.</b>

293
00:27:44,210 --> 00:27:45,350
<b>Oh, boy.</b>

294
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:48,240
<b>- Hello, Eun Sil. - What?</b>

295
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:51,290
<b>- What a very casual entrance. - Wasn't it?</b>

296
00:27:51,350 --> 00:27:54,720
<b>Gosh, our timing is finally right for a change.</b>

297
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:55,920
<b>I know.</b>

298
00:27:57,650 --> 00:27:59,690
<b>Look at those roses.</b>

299
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:03,930
<b>Hey. Aren't these...</b>

300
00:28:03,930 --> 00:28:06,630
<b>the same ones you gave me a long time ago?</b>

301
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,200
<b>What?</b>

302
00:28:10,330 --> 00:28:11,540
<b>What...</b>

303
00:28:11,970 --> 00:28:14,010
<b>Are you asking me out like this?</b>

304
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,400
<b>Yes.</b>

305
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:18,310
<b>I'm Lee Jang Woo, the student body president.</b>

306
00:28:18,310 --> 00:28:21,550
<b>- I know that you're Lee Jang Woo. - You know me?</b>

307
00:28:22,180 --> 00:28:23,750
<b>Those roses are white.</b>

308
00:28:23,910 --> 00:28:28,120
<b>You must be very kind and innocent, right?</b>

309
00:28:28,120 --> 00:28:29,320
<b>Yes, I am.</b>

310
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,350
<b>But that's too bad.</b>

311
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:35,560
<b>Baek Gyeong asked me out during lunch earlier today.</b>

312
00:28:35,820 --> 00:28:37,270
<b>And I said yes.</b>

313
00:28:37,490 --> 00:28:38,630
<b>What?</b>

314
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:40,200
<b>Sorry.</b>

315
00:28:41,800 --> 00:28:44,410
<b>- I guess our timing didn't match. - Timing?</b>

316
00:28:45,570 --> 00:28:48,510
<b>- What is that? - It's nothing.</b>

317
00:28:48,570 --> 00:28:50,410
<b>- Can I read it? - No, you can't. Why?</b>

318
00:28:50,410 --> 00:28:52,810
<b>Don't take it. Put that back down. Why?</b>

319
00:28:53,170 --> 00:28:55,380
<b>- Thank you. - But that's not for you. Why?</b>

320
00:28:55,380 --> 00:28:57,610
<b>- Put that back down. - But I'll have to say no.</b>

321
00:28:57,610 --> 00:28:59,890
<b>- I said no. - What?</b>

322
00:29:00,320 --> 00:29:02,020
<b>Guys, I said no, okay?</b>

323
00:29:02,020 --> 00:29:04,020
<b>Eun Sil, that letter... Eun Sil, the letter!</b>

324
00:29:04,020 --> 00:29:06,550
<b>- Give me the letter. Eun Sil! - He got rejected.</b>

325
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:10,260
<b>- He got rejected! - She said no!</b>

326
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:12,290
<b>When did you guys come?</b>

327
00:29:12,290 --> 00:29:14,660
<b>- She said no. - How embarrassing.</b>

328
00:29:14,660 --> 00:29:17,570
<b>- Where are you going? - He got rejected!</b>

329
00:29:18,830 --> 00:29:20,110
<b>Then...</b>

330
00:29:20,570 --> 00:29:22,700
<b>if you didn't go out with Baek Gyeong back then...</b>

331
00:29:22,700 --> 00:29:24,540
<b>- Of course, I would've said no. - Right?</b>

332
00:29:24,540 --> 00:29:27,880
<b>Yes. You weren't my type back then. Not at all.</b>

333
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:31,780
<b>I was attracted to bad boys back then.</b>

334
00:29:31,780 --> 00:29:33,150
<b>Bad boys?</b>

335
00:29:33,150 --> 00:29:35,520
<b>I guess Baek Gyeong was kind of bad.</b>

336
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:37,520
<b>I heard you're going somewhere nice later.</b>

337
00:29:37,520 --> 00:29:39,890
<b>- Somewhere nice? - Yes, I'm going to follow you.</b>

338
00:29:39,890 --> 00:29:41,460
<b>It's going to be fun.</b>

339
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:43,190
<b>Follow me where?</b>

340
00:29:43,190 --> 00:29:47,700
<b>I've already put in a word, okay?</b>

341
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:52,270
<b>Eun Sil? Eun Sil.</b>

342
00:29:53,070 --> 00:29:54,840
<b>- Eun Sil. - Hey!</b>

343
00:29:54,840 --> 00:29:56,040
<b>Hi, Ji Young.</b>

344
00:29:56,040 --> 00:29:58,240
<b>- Hello. - Hey, you can have some too.</b>

345
00:29:58,240 --> 00:30:00,580
<b>- It's all right. - Okay.</b>

346
00:30:00,580 --> 00:30:02,610
<b>- I'm here. - Hi, come in.</b>

347
00:30:02,610 --> 00:30:04,880
<b>This radish water kimchi is perfectly ripe and delicious.</b>

348
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:07,720
<b>- Goodness, that looks good. - Come try some.</b>

349
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:09,980
<b>- Thank you so much. - Sure.</b>

350
00:30:09,980 --> 00:30:12,990
<b>It's so warm in here. Can you make me some sesame oil?</b>

351
00:30:12,990 --> 00:30:15,290
<b>Okay, I'll make it, so come pick it up tomorrow.</b>

352
00:30:15,290 --> 00:30:16,990
<b>Okay, thanks.</b>

353
00:30:16,990 --> 00:30:19,730
<b>By the way, did you hear?</b>

354
00:30:19,730 --> 00:30:21,260
<b>Hear what?</b>

355
00:30:21,260 --> 00:30:23,770
<b>The daughter of Hodu House came here.</b>

356
00:30:23,770 --> 00:30:26,030
<b>The daughter of that family always lived there.</b>

357
00:30:26,030 --> 00:30:27,600
<b>No, not her.</b>

358
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:30,010
<b>You know, the daughter...</b>

359
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:35,250
<b>You know, the daughter who killed her husband.</b>

360
00:30:36,010 --> 00:30:37,550
<b>Can you believe it?</b>

361
00:30:37,550 --> 00:30:40,350
<b>How can she come back here after doing that to her husband?</b>

362
00:30:40,350 --> 00:30:43,420
<b>Well, the women from that family are all so spiteful.</b>

363
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:45,720
<b>Even their mom was spiteful.</b>

364
00:30:45,720 --> 00:30:48,790
<b>Both her daughters were just like her.</b>

365
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:52,070
<b>How spiteful could one be to kill her own husband...</b>

366
00:30:53,390 --> 00:30:57,510
<b>Right, weren't you close with her granddaughter?</b>

367
00:30:57,830 --> 00:31:00,270
<b>Bo Yeong, what are you doing? Go to your room.</b>

368
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:03,850
<b>No, I need to go to the academy. Bye.</b>

369
00:31:17,650 --> 00:31:18,990
<b>You promised me...</b>

370
00:31:19,750 --> 00:31:23,560
<b>not to tell anyone either.</b>

371
00:31:26,690 --> 00:31:28,360
<b>I trusted Joo Hee.</b>

372
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:30,410
<b>And I trusted you.</b>

373
